      <p>PHIVOLCS is a service institute of the DOST. The agency is tasked to mitigate disasters that may arise from volcanic eruptions, earthquakes, tsunami and other related geotectonic phenomena.</p>
      <p>Contact Details:
      <ul>
        <li>Website: phivolcs.dost.gov.ph
