      <h3>Project NOAH</h3>
      <p>The Nationwide Operational Assessment of Hazards (NOAH) is a program launched by the DOST to put in place a responsive program for disaster prevention and mitigation, using advanced technology to enhance current geo-hazard vulnerability maps.</p>
      <p>Contact Details:
      <ul>
        <li>The Project NOAH web portal is located at noah.dost.gov.ph.
      </ul>
      </p>

